flowRoot.flowPara: The workflow to evaluate a harmonization technique. The input data are an image dataset (a), a mask (b) selecting voxels to include, and a table (c) associating images to groups (such as study site) over which to remove effeects. Our tool provides two modules: harmonization (d) and report generation (e). A harmonization technique is configured (d) and an analysis of site effects is conducted (e), producing reports of the significance and size of site effects before (f) and after (g) harmonization.
